Name: Classic Margherita Pizza
Description: A simple and delicious Italian pizza topped with fresh tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, and basil leaves, often baked in a wood-fired oven.

Name: Beef Stroganoff
Description: A creamy and savory Russian dish made with tender strips of beef, mushrooms, and onions, served over egg noodles or rice.

Name: Chicken Tikka Masala
Description: A flavorful Indian-inspired dish featuring marinated chicken cooked in a creamy, spiced tomato sauce, typically served with rice or naan.

Name: Spaghetti Carbonara
Description: A classic Italian pasta dish made with spaghetti, eggs, Parmesan cheese, and pancetta, creating a creamy, savory sauce.

Name: Thai Green Curry
Description: A spicy and aromatic Thai curry with green chilies, coconut milk, and a variety of fresh vegetables, typically served with rice.

Name: French Onion Soup
Description: A rich and hearty soup made with caramelized onions, beef broth, and topped with melted cheese on toasted bread.

Name: Beef Wellington
Description: A luxurious British dish featuring tender beef fillet coated with mushroom duxelles and wrapped in puff pastry, baked until golden.

Name: Vegetable Stir Fry
Description: A quick, healthy dish with a variety of fresh vegetables stir-fried in a savory sauce, often served over rice or noodles.

Name: Chocolate Lava Cake
Description: A decadent dessert with a rich chocolate cake exterior and a warm, gooey, melted chocolate center.

Name: Greek Moussaka
Description: A classic Greek casserole with layers of eggplant, ground beef or lamb, and a creamy béchamel sauce, baked to perfection.

Name: Fish and Chips
Description: A traditional British dish of battered and fried fish served with crispy, thick-cut fries, often with tartar sauce or malt vinegar.

Name: Caesar Salad
Description: A classic salad with romaine lettuce, Parmesan cheese, croutons, and a tangy Caesar dressing, often topped with grilled chicken.

Name: Mushroom Risotto
Description: A creamy Italian rice dish cooked with mushrooms, garlic, and Parmesan cheese, creating a rich, earthy flavor.

Name: Apple Pie
Description: A beloved dessert with a buttery crust filled with spiced, sweet-tart apples, baked until golden brown and often served with ice cream.

Name: Beef Tacos
Description: Soft or crispy tortillas filled with seasoned ground beef, topped with lettuce, cheese, and salsa.

Name: Pad Thai
Description: A popular Thai stir-fried noodle dish with shrimp or chicken, peanuts, eggs, and a tangy sauce made from tamarind and fish sauce.

Name: Chicken Parmesan
Description: Breaded chicken breast topped with marinara sauce and melted mozzarella, served over pasta or on its own.

Name: Carrot Cake
Description: A moist, spiced cake made with grated carrots and topped with cream cheese frosting, often including walnuts or raisins.

Name: Shepherd's Pie
Description: A comforting British dish of ground lamb or beef with vegetables in gravy, topped with mashed potatoes and baked until golden.

Name: Eggs Benedict
Description: A classic breakfast dish featuring poached eggs and Canadian bacon on an English muffin, topped with hollandaise sauce.
